race.comment: VOODOO LASS (7) resumes here but the form she showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Tuned up for this with a recent trial win and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. MISTER BIANCO (1) is one from one over this track and trip and will strip fitter second-up from the spell. Expected to feature with the 3kg claim. CUTEPI (4) was a touch disappointing last time out but the three runs prior were full of merit. Worth another chance. BLUE SPINEL (3) is improving with racing this campaign and will be ready to peak now. In the mix. STARSARISE (6) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
